{
  "stem": "26111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, at least one, one that I could remember very, very well because it really imprinted itself on my child mind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I-- when I was about nine, maybe younger, I was-- I fell ill with diphtheria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was rather sudden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father took me to the hospital, which they-- where he was a consultant, a medical consultant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And outside of his private practice, he apparently was also a consultant to one or two hospitals and clinics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the private rooms were all full.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I had to go into the children's ward, the general ward, where there maybe-- I don't know-- 20, 30, 40 children, side by side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at first, all was quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there just sort of was the usual childish banter among them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know anybody, so I just lay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was too sick to take part, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then some bright spark looked on my nameplate and saw that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's when the fun began.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at the-- I don't think I spent a-- the, the, the decibel level in that room was such that nurses and even one time, a doctor, I remember, came in, indignant, you know, children, children!",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You  must-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when they heard, however, that they were-- all they were shouting was 'Christ killer' and-- this was around Christmastime, I should add-- and, and, and the various anti-Jewish things, then they were-- they became much more smiling [LAUGHS] and, oh, well, children will be children.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "However-- that was one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In other words, continuous jeering and, and shouting and insults, nothing physical.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were nurses on duty, and, well--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left, that was almost the worst moment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
